title: The Intruder
description: In this Dateline classic, local police and the FBI find themselves working side by side on a curious investigation when a violent home invasion rocks a small town in Maine. Andrea Canning reports. Originally aired on NBC on June 2, 2017.
author: nbcnews.podcasts@gmail.com (NBC News)
